# results/.gitkeep
# Subdirectories (rnn/, lstm/, gru/, bilstm/) and their artefacts are
# created at runtime by trainer.hyperparameter_search().
# Generated files per architecture:
#   best_model.pth      – best checkpoint (state dict + metadata)
#   tuning_results.csv  – full grid search results sorted by avg_val_f1
#   experiment.log      – timestamped training log
